{"tid":1077183,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解日本人唔興飲朱古力奶？","createTime":"2019-03-25T11:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T16:30:15.000Z","uid":198607,"like":7,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"453d5bc82c682a7a79daec3cbaed88bffe64e464","tid":1077183,"uid":198607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:58:36.000Z","msg":"試過之前有次係日本便利店 有個鬼妹走嚟問我盒野係咪朱古力奶 我見係啡色 答咗佢係 之後自己買嚟試 發覺原來係咖啡嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好意思呀<br />\n<br />\n之後每次都會攞起盒啡色包裝疑似朱古力奶既野飲 飲個下先會知原來又係咖啡嚟 不過又真係幾好飲嘅<br />\n<br />\n點解好似真係無盒裝朱古力奶買咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申唔識日文 試過曬咁多盒疑似朱古奶咁濟 點知都係咖啡 雖然都係幾好飲 但無知一問 係咪真係無盒裝朱古力奶？"},{"pid":"3f746d780bd3d0eb0574ef8e7413b35f773221ed","tid":1077183,"uid":198607,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nYKs2G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nYKs2G.png&h=1dbacd91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e387b218f48bd53ac20c716d2f2373c07e4761b9","tid":1077183,"uid":77637,"like":69,"dislike":2,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:01:44.000Z","msg":"咖啡Corner搵牛奶？"},{"pid":"23076fd7f4f97ffa7336ec3ebddec25240d24302","tid":1077183,"uid":51747,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3f746d780bd3d0eb0574ef8e7413b35f773221ed","tid":1077183,"uid":198607,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nYKs2G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nYKs2G.png&h=1dbacd91&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:02:47.000Z","msg":"左下可可幾好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4ed26a7f4ee6d02c8960951d5c34ad3ba9fc02","tid":1077183,"uid":1977,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:04:58.000Z"